------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Lesson 37 语法讲解

+ 一般将来时
    计划、打算、对未来的打算

    句型：be going to
    A.何时用?      预先计划和打算要做的事。
    B.固定形式      主 + is\am\are + going to
    C.小小的要求     后面接动词原形
        I am gonna be happy this year.

        口语中：be going to = be gonna

        be going to do \ be going to be + adj. n. prep. ...


    我打算下周开始忙起来了。
    I am going be busy next week.

    他计划这周呆在家里。
    He is going to be at home this weekend.

    这个孩子打算以后成为医生。
    The kid is going to be a doctor.

    我打算周末去逛街
    I am going to go shopping this weekend.

    他打算把旧车卖了买辆新的。
    He is going to sell his old car,and buy a new one.

    D.be going to 句型的其他形式
        疑问：be 提前
        否定：be + not

        她打算周末去逛街。
        She is going to go shopping this weekend.

        Is she going to go shopping this weekend?
        She is not going to go shopping this weekend.

