Lesson 37 课文讲解

+ You are working hard,...      你正在努力工作。
    你正忙着呢!

+ Give me...

+ I'm going to paint it(the bookcase) pink.
  主           谓    宾               宾语补足语

  助动词

  宾补：对宾语的补充和说明，使句子更加简洁。

  我发现那屋子是黑的
  I find the room dark.

  大家务必保持教室的干净
  We must keep the classroom clean.

  历史使人明知    Histories make men wise.

  诗歌使灵秀。    Poems make men witty.

  数学使人缜密     Math make men subtle.

  哲学使人深刻    Philosophy make men deep.


+ It's for my daughter.

    for：
    A.为了...某人而...        It's for you
    B.对于某人来说            Math is so difficult for me.
    C.表原因                  What are you sorry for?
    D.长达                    I study Yoga for two years.

