Lesson 37 单词讲解

+ work          工作. v.
    I work in NO School.

+ hard          努力地. adv.副词
    A.副词的功能：用来修饰adj.\v.\adv.

    修饰 adj.
        I am tired.
        I am ver tired.
        I am so tired.
        I am too tired.
        I am awfully tired.

    修饰 v.
        I love you.
        I love you very much.
        I love you awfully.

    修饰 adv.

    B.副词的位置：通常情况，形前动后
        I swim well.        我游泳游的很好。
        I know him well.    我很了解他。

    C.hard词性讨论：努力地 adv. 勤奋的/艰苦的 adj.
        hard work       艰苦的工作
        work hard       努力的工作

程度副词

+ make          做
    What make is it?        这是什么牌子？
    make the bed            整理床铺
    make a bookcase\bookshelf   制作一个书架

+ bookcase      书架
+ hammer        锤子
+ paint         涂色，上色
+ painting      画
+ Chinese paintings     国画
+ pink          粉色
+ favourite     最喜欢的
+ favorite      最喜欢的
    favorite  color\city\school\book\girl
    What's your favorite...?

